description: [``botocore``] This release adds the LastUpdatedDate and LastUsedDate timestamps to help you manage your cost allocation tags.
[``botocore``] Global Accelerator now supports Client Ip Preservation for Network Load Balancer endpoints.
[``botocore``] Adding parameters to CreateCustomDbEngineVersion reserved for future use.
[``botocore``] Documentation updates for Amazon Verified Permissions. Increases max results per page for ListPolicyStores, ListPolicies, and ListPolicyTemplates APIs from 20 to 50.
